s://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brian_johnson_knopfler-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brian_johnson_knopfler-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brian_johnson_knopfler-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/acdc">AC/DC</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-johnson">布莱恩·约翰逊</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dire-straits">Dire Straits</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-knopfler">马克·诺普弗勒</a>将主演一部新的纪录片系列，名为<i>《约翰逊和诺普弗勒的音乐传奇》</i> 。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="379" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/ac-dc-comeback-album-power-up-interview-malcolm-young-woke-2800458"><b>AC/DC 谈他们爆炸性的复出唱片《Power Up》：“这张专辑是献给 Malcolm 的”</b></a></li></ul><p>这部由六部分组成的系列节目将见证两位经典摇滚歌手探索另外六位音乐传奇人物的生活，该节目将于 4 月 25 日起在天空艺术频道每周播出。</p><p>约翰逊和诺普弗勒将在每一集中分别审视<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-jones">汤姆·琼斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">萨姆·芬德</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cyndi-lauper">辛迪·劳珀</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nile-rodgers">尼罗·罗杰斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/carlos-santana">卡洛斯·桑塔纳</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/emmylou-harris">埃米卢·哈里斯</a>的职业生涯，主持人还会在剧集中与嘉宾进行现场表演。 </p><figure id="attachment_2805674" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2805674" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-2805674" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-cont